videoSnippet.title: In Honor and Memory of Vugar Gashimov - The Pride of Azerbaijan
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Check out an artice on Gashimov from NY Times https://www.nytimes.com/2014/01/13/crosswords/chess/vugar-gashimov-27-azerbaijan-chess-grandmaster-dies.html

Wiki on Gashimov https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vugar_Gashimov

Check out the Official Page of Shamkir Chess http://shamkirchess.com/

Anish Giri vs Vugar Gashimov
Tata Steel (2012), Wijk aan Zee NED, rd 8, Jan-22 
Sicilian Defense: Najdorf Variation (B94)
